description:
for the ones who can't run Netbeans on 22.04 :
the reason is because " Cannot find java. Please use the --jdkhome switch." 
so you basically have to reinstall OpenJDK using : sudo apt install openjdk-xx-jdk (the XX means the version of OpenJDK)

Ctrl+t (Abrimos la terminal)
...
//Escribimos lo siguiente:
sudo apt update &&upgrade
//aplicamos enter, escribimos lo siguiente:
sudo apt install netbeans
//Aplicamos enter, Escribimos por ultimo:
netbeans
//Aolicamos enter.
exit
aplicamos exit
